      {
        "title": "Capture relays on scan",
        "body": "On capture relays, enter your faction and the site code from the sticker. Holds decay unless your team reinforces — network points on the city board sum location weights, not personal scan counts."
      },
      {
        "title": "Fog on the city board",
        "body": "The schematic board shows owned relays, rumored hints, and cooperative nodes — not every unclaimed relay. Use Places by district below for full wayfinding."
      }
